::Firearm/Smokescreen::

Firearm stops Smokescreen as the Maximal gets up to follow Spears. "Stay 
here, I'll go. I need to get back to base anyways."

Smokescreen nods as Firearm exits, following Lunarpine and Spears. "You'll 
need to be put into stasis lock before entering the Cybertronian Fire," he 
says as he walks up to them, "Whatever the Trainers did to you may still be 
functional, it could endanger the Maximals."
